Class Feedback

java.lang.Object
main.Feedback
public class Feedback extends Object
Represents a feedback message in the system. This class contains all the properties of a feedback message including its ID, sender, receiver, content, timestamp, question ID, answer ID, review ID, and parent message ID.

    • Feedback

      public Feedback(int feedbackId, String sender, String receiver, String content, Date timestamp, int questionId, Integer answerId, Integer reviewId, Integer parentMessageId)
      Constructs a new Feedback object with the specified properties.
      Parameters:
      feedbackId - The ID of the feedback message
      sender - The username of the sender
      receiver - The username of the receiver
      content - The content of the feedback message
      timestamp - The timestamp of when the feedback was created
      questionId - The ID of the question this feedback belongs to
      answerId - The ID of the answer this feedback belongs to (nullable)
      reviewId - The ID of the review this feedback belongs to (nullable)
      parentMessageId - The ID of the parent message in a threaded conversation (nullable)
